Trade/Device Name(s): IMMAGE Immunochemistry System Low Concentration Immunoglobulin M (IGMLC) Reagent
IMMAGE Immunochemistry System Cerebrospinal Fluid Protein Calibrator (CSF CAL)
Regulation Name(s): Immunoglobulins A, G, M, D, and E immunological test system
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for IMMAGE Immunochemistry System IGMLC Reagent and CSF Protein Calibrator for quantitative determination of immunoglobulin M in serum and CSF using rate nephelometry
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative determination of immunoglobulin M in human serum or cerebrospinal fluid using rate nephelometry in conjunction with IMMAGE Immunochemistry Systems and CSF Protein Calibrator
